3.4 R TIDYVERSE 

split_by_species <-
  crickets %>%
  group_nest(species)
split_by_species
model_by_species <-
  split_by_species %>%
  mutate(model = map(data, ~ lm(rate ~ temp, data = .x)))
model_by_species
model_by_species %>%
  mutate(coef = map(model, tidy)) %>%
  select(species, coef) %>%
  unnest(coef)
